{"tid":1144915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小學收生不足面臨縮班　法國家長帶綿羊報名「湊數」","createTime":"2019-05-08T10:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T11:09:41.000Z","uid":75969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0957ccdfc8ca7fade5130c6c7e985634e5fdb8b6","tid":1144915,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190508/s00005/e3bcf5dae03666230e3e42153ae9265e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190508%2Fs00005%2Fe3bcf5dae03666230e3e42153ae9265e.jpg&h=e557c864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國阿爾卑斯山區域一所小學的家長擔心該校收生不足面臨縮班，周二（7日）牽了15隻羊去報名「湊數」。<br />\n<br />\n上述小學位於法國境內阿爾卑斯山腳的貝勒多訥山嶺（Crets en Belledonne），因為學生人數由266名減至261名，全校原來的11班需要縮減一班，引起家長憂慮。周二早上，有當地牧民帶着狗驅趕一群共約50頭羊，浩浩蕩蕩到該校「報名」入讀。<br />\n<br />\n其中的15頭羊因有出生證明，獲「正式」註冊就學，且由「咩咩叫貝特」和「跳跳羊」兩頭羊代表「新生」，在全校師生、家長見證下，舉行搞笑入學典禮。<br />\n<br />\n策劃此行動的學生家長拉瓦爾（Gaelle Laval）批評國家教育部門光看重收生人數，而非學生福祉。他說，就是要用幽默手法喚醒大家對可悲情况的關注，他笑着說﹕「我們現在不用殺班了。」<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190508/s00005/1557307773375/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190508%2Fs00005%2F1557307773375%2F&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2Fct5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=94f61535\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190508%2Fs00005%2F1557307773375%2F&h=58c33c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190508/s00005/1557307773375/</a>"},{"pid":"17d6d5e7e3c2fbd54c2ec80f27698c1052960275","tid":1144915,"uid":251666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c9f9e4cc90a890a0cb83664321b72a6b176d9a4","tid":1144915,"uid":251666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}